text: Fabian Kwok (born 17 March 1989) is a Singaporean professional footballer who currently plays for Hougang United in the S.League. He plays as a midfielder. ==Career== Fabian Kwok played in the S.League for Tampines Rovers, Geylang International, Young Lions FC and currently Hougang United.
